      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COASTAL COWBOY (2) resumes and now in the Tony & Maddysen Sears yard. Failed to get into the contest on debut with a poor sixth over 1200m at the Gold Coast last November. Ran fourth in a 1000m trial at the Gold Coast and can sprint well fresh with the blinkers going on. SAVANNA GOLDEN BOY (10) finds a much easier contest and back in trip after finishing fourth over 1600m at Wyong. Assess on the run three-back when placing over 1200m at Gosford. Each-way prospect. BASSETT'S CHOICE (6) well bred filly yet to fire in six career starts. Back in trip and grade after fading late to finish fourth over 1800m at Eagle Farm. Comes here in peak condition and quickly running out of chances.  EASY TRAPEZEE (4) improved performance at his second race start when sent forward for a plugging fourth over 1300m at Tuncurry. Finds a weak contest and can take a hand in the finish from the draw.",
